{"type": "article", "id": 19418, "title": "带夹层的椅子", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-21T07:40:56Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021347397x5MtlTN4dH3h8Qe.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是来自韩国设计师 SOHYUN YUN 的带夹层的椅子，是用透明的亚克力做的。靠背和座位面都是空心的，可以插进去 3 层亚克力板、印花或者其他带图案的平面材料。当不同的图案前后排列时，能显示出奇妙的重叠效果，它尤其适合安迪·沃霍尔的广告画，让同一种图形有不同的深浅变化。<a href=\"http://luckandmiracle.wix.com/designersohyunyun#!layer-project/c1mqf\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145916CyNnWFurzVAi6dlM.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261459175GDXKq7u9f6AUV4M.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145917cf31PM69UHZyKkqs.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261459181kEFpqr49b2ds6oy.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145918hF7ij2CzG5V8wug1.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}